*Gledali* smo film zajedno (We watched a movie together).
Mi *gledamo* televiziju svakog dana (We watch TV every day).
Oni *gleda* na nebo (They are looking at the sky).
Ona je *gledala* knjigu (She was reading a book).
Ja sam *gledao* u tebe (I was looking at you).
Oni su *gledali* jedni druge (They were looking at each other).